{"tid":2220040,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows XP 源碼網上流出　Microsoft 正調查事件","createTime":"2020-09-27T10:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T16:43:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8a95d2949f48ecfa7bf409bc042b5cf6d0790202","tid":2220040,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:35:38.000Z","msg":"對於軟件開發商而言，其產品的源碼是其相當珍貴的資產，特別是像 Windows 這樣的操作系統就更甚。最近有駭客將 Windows XP 等多個系統的源碼完整公開，引起關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/windows-xp-1280x640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fwindows-xp-1280x640.jpg&h=282297c3&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n在 4chan 論壇上被公開源碼的系統包括有 MS DOS 3.30、MS DOS 6.0、Windows 2000、Windows CE 3、Windows CE 4、Windows CE 5、Windows Embedded 7、Windows Embedded CE、Windows NT 3.5、Windows NT 4、Windows Server 2003 和 Windows XP SP1，總共多達 43GB。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/09/26/the-windows-xp-source-code-was-allegedly-leaked-online/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F09%2F26%2Fthe-windows-xp-source-code-was-allegedly-leaked-online%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=34b6d6d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/09/26/the-windows-xp-source-code-was-allegedly-leaked-online/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"12521671224daa23fa7386c20525ff434c7a1748","tid":2220040,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:36:09.000Z","msg":"除了 Windows 的源碼之外，駭客亦加入了有關 Bill Gates 的陰謀論影片，似是對他的控訴。駭客表示，Windows XP 的源碼其實已經在駭客群體中流傳多年，不過今次是首次向公衆公開。不過 Microsoft 方面雖然表示正在調查事件，但並未有確認源碼是否真正的 Windows 源碼。之前 Windows 10 的內部版本也曾經在 2017 年洩漏源碼，這樣的源碼洩漏有機會導致保安問題，特別是如果當時使用的源碼存在漏洞而至今仍然有效，則有機會被利用作入侵。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/xp-source-code-torrent.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fxp-source-code-torrent.jpg&h=b81ff167&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"},{"pid":"f35ae103dee5ddb105caeb5da931d5fff3754961","tid":2220040,"uid":17443,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:37:19.000Z","msg":"好快有自煮研發新系統出現"},{"pid":"8ac67d66812f92ea2b04b50b6edf65e0eecfbf8c","tid":2220040,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:37:53.000Z","msg":"中國可以自煮燃髪電腦os<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a9668adcaf8581c214eabbd78d5072b3a65724","tid":2220040,"uid":180184,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"仲調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十幾年前M$為左打入中國市場, 開源比中國信息安全測評中心, <br />\n隨後幾年開始流出source code, 一堆漏洞從來無fix過, <br />\nWindows login 使用者密碼對於一班睇開source code既人形同虛設 <br />\ne.g. 入個系統還原模式改幾個files已經可以隨便改人密碼hack入部機<br />\n呢D仲要去到Windows 10都仲未fix 好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7aNyB0V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7aNyB0V.jpg&h=33cabce1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bcf4788640ef137a81d9688c5b9f7ef937b58de","tid":2220040,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"黑客將會 全！面！進！場！"},{"pid":"e23d594c3382b554770252b86ef8d02513a6043e","tid":2220040,"uid":375148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"其實應該冇人想要？ xp 十年前科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利息 9up"},{"pid":"c8d07454233